{
  "stem": "6258.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--two walls, in between two walls here, how do you call it?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This little--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Corner, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "See?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Corner.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I went into my little corner in my room, and I wrote a poem.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I wrote a poem about this-- that it is-- it's very easy to complain all the time how we are being harmed, and how everything is terrible, and what to do.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And maybe we should run away, maybe we shouldn't.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This is easy.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But what is not easy is, against all odds, to get up and keep clear mind and hope that something will change and look over the walls into the sun.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And you see, now while I was transcribing my diary-- well, into here, in Cambridge, into, on, on my typewriter-- I look at this poem.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I thought, my goodness, for the first time, I noticed here that my inner resistance was born.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Then, because I was trying not to give in to the despair, to everything, that it is absolutely important to keep that inner strength.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But there was a Jewish resistance.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I knew that it's there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But there was no way of getting.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "First of all, I was too young.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Number two, you cannot just go and join them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You have to be taken by them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And people who were there, and now I know that they were many of our friends, they were not-- they were very careful not to talk because they were afraid of the German and others collaborators.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because there were Jewish collaborators, too, shame to say, but there were.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So-- but one whom I know and who was wonderful, really, when I talked to him once, and I thought he looked-- remember that I want also do something, I want to be useful.",
      "word_count": 34
    }
  ],
